- **Initial load failure is a dead end for QR users** - lines 40-46. After a transient network failure, the page only shows text and gives the guest no retry action. In a restaurant QR flow that forces a hard refresh instead of an in-page recovery path. Suggested fix:

  ```jsx
  {error && (
    <div role="alert" className="space-y-3">
      <p className="text-red-500">{error}</p>
      <button type="button" onClick={fetchItems}>
        {t('common.retry')}
      </button>
    </div>
  )}
  ```

## Low Priority (P3) - Nice to Have

None.

## Open Questions / Assumptions

- **`useI18n` import path is inconsistent with the rest of this repo** - line 2 uses `@/components/useI18n`, while the nearby pages in this checkout consistently use `@/components/i18n`. I did not count this as a confirmed defect because the shared i18n module is not present in this repository snapshot, so I could not verify which alias exists in the live Base44 project.

