+    setError(null);
+    try {
+      // ...
+      setItems(data);
+    } catch {
+      setError(t('test_page.error.load_failed'));
+    }
+  };
+  ```
+
+- **Initial load failure is a dead end for QR users** - lines 40-46. After a transient network failure, the page only shows text and gives the guest no retry action. In a restaurant QR flow that forces a hard refresh instead of an in-page recovery path. Suggested fix:
+
